Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.30,0:23:03.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怒视着全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那双眼睛在说
